    <introduction>
        <p>Having just learned more about exponents, including negative exponents, we can discuss a format used for very large and very small numbers called <term>scientific notation</term>.</p>
         <figure>
            <caption>Alternative Video Lesson</caption>
            <video youtubelist="PLmuZCPhWPt-eUYq3sBms_5CaAqWvayULV" />
        </figure>
